            <thetext>If a textfield is in a window, selecting text within the textfield with the mouse only works if the window is not dragged to another position.

After the window was moved, the cursor is stuck and you cannot mark text anymore by mouse (cursor keys still work).

Example:
Qooxdoo Demo Browser -&gt; Demo -&gt; table -&gt; Table Window Editor

Double click a number -&gt; select text within the textfield by dragging the mouse -&gt; works
Move the Cell Editor Window -&gt; text selection by mouse does not work anymore</thetext>
